<html>
  <head>
    <title></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <span style="margin-left: 47%;">
      <img alt="" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/resume/image/upload/c_scale,w_50/v1427155934/crescent_green_rt6rit.png" />
    </span>
    <hr style="color:#999999">
    <p>
      <span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', 'lucida grande', arial, verdana, 'lucida sans unicode', tahoma, sans-serif;">
        Hi <%= @user.first_name.blank? ? '' : @user.first_name.split(' ')[0] %>,
      </span>
    </p>

    <p>
      <span style="font-family: 'Open Sans', 'lucida grande', arial, verdana, 'lucida sans unicode', tahoma, sans-serif;">
        My name is Joe, and I’m the Career Advisor for <%= @school.upcase %>. I’m writing to invite you to try Meed, a career marketplace for students.
        More than <%= number_with_delimiter(@school_user_count, :delimiter => ',') %> from <%= @school.upcase %> are already using Meed to connect with recruiters from top companies and hot startups like
        <a href="https://getmeed.com/company/spotify#about">Spotify</a>,
        <a href="https://getmeed.com/company/quora#about">Quora</a>,
        <a href="https://getmeed.com/company/6sense#about">6Sense</a>, and tons more.
        <br/><br/>
        Use Meed to choose courses, skills, and projects that are inline with you career goals.
        Ask recruiters, alumni, and your peers questions on everything from what hairstyles are interview appropriate to answering the dreaded “tell me about yourself?”
      </span>
    </p>

    <div style="margin-top:5px"></div>

    <div class="btn" style="Margin-bottom: 21px;padding-bottom: 2px;text-align: center">
      <!--[if !mso]-->
      <a style="background-image: url(https://i3.createsend1.com/static/eb/master/05-slate/images/btn.png);background-repeat: repeat-x;background-position: left top;border-radius: 3px;display: inline-block;font-size: 13px;font-weight: 700;line-height: 19px;padding: 6px 18px 5px 18px;text-align: center;text-decoration: none;transition: all 0.2s;color: #fff;font-family: 'Open Sans', 'lucida grande', arial, verdana, 'lucida sans unicode', tahoma, sans-serif;background-color: #5cb85c;border-color: #4cae4c; text-shadow: 0 1px 0 0 1px 0 #172027" href="https://getmeed.com?e_var=eiuv2" target="_blank">
        Sign Up
      </a>
      <!--[endif]-->
      <!--[if mso]>
